Description: Hi, I have for Auction a brand new s/steel Ladies 'SCAT Classic' Sports watch with Black face. Watch comes in a lovely Scat Classic display box and with a 2year warranty.(Covered by an Australian Company). The full Stainless steel construction and water resistancy of this watch makes it a great everyday watch.
